data.description: Welcome to the highly sought after private gated Community of Four Seasons 55+, a beautiful little Oasis located in the city of Beaumont! This immaculate 2 bedroom 2 bathroom Home is situated at the end of the street, conveniently located near walking trails, community amenities, and ease of access from the guarded front gate. This 1556 sq ft single story Home offers ample living space, bonus room/office space, indoor laundry facilities, an attached 2 car garage with storage rafters, a gated front courtyard, and the primary bedroom has a generously sized walk in closet and it?s own attached bathroom. If you?re looking for a turnkey, ready to love Home, this is it! Don?t miss out on the amenities that Four Seasons has to offer its residents and guests! Living in this gorgeous Community you can take advantage of the large outdoor Sports Complex spanning over 10 acres that includes an outdoor pool with a lovely patio and barbecue area, tennis, pickleball, basketball and bocce ball courts. Also, located in the Four Seasons community in Beaumont are two recreation centers perfect for maintaining your active lifestyle! Don?t miss out on your opportunity to call this House, Home!
